                    <l n="4">ne<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭ<choice><sic>u</sic><corr>i</corr></choice> t<choice><sic>u</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>y<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>a</corr></choice>l <choice><sic>ā</sic><corr>ū</corr></choice>ḻiyuḷ Iṭaituṟai nāṭum</l>
                    <l n="5">tuṭarvaṉa vēli-p paṭarvaṉa vāciyu <lb n="4" break="no"/>ñ</l>
